WHO   — Paul Atreides — Muad'Dib, the Kwisatz Haderach
WHAT  — The son of Duke Leto and the Bene Gesserit Jessica, who becomes Muad'Dib, the Fremen messiah.
WHERE — D1 · Dune  Framework inputs: The Kwisatz Haderach — the messianic line of House Atreides on Arrakis  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — He topples the Padishah Emperor and seizes the throne, then recoils from the jihad his name unleashes across the galaxy.
HOW   — Trained as a near-Mentat and in the Bene Gesserit ways, awakened by the spice melange to bridge space and time and see all possible futures.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  The boy who could see every future, and could not bear the one his name had made.

